snippet.title: Starlight Shores Release Trailer (Visual Novel)
snippet.description:
Free demo available here: https://tidalblossoms.itch.io/starlight-shores

Starlight Shores is an island-themed romance game. 

Your best friend Theo is celebrating your birthday with a seaside getaway. Party with your friends under the stars, and watch sparks fly!

Launching October 30th, 2020... 

Music Credit- Arrival by MBB

https://spoti.fi/2wqzjwK
https://soundcloud.com/mbbofficial
https://twitter.com/mbbmusic
